          "reviewBody": "Very good CBSC school in Pune . They have many branches.  We opt their old brach Nigdi . This schhol.have less space fir play ground but they tried their best for take care on play and education at same time.\nEducation pattern is slightly different than other CBSC school.whichbwe observed and this help students to clear the concept . You cab take French or Hindi as optional language . They will give books in every quarterly and PTM , Direct interaction with Priciple ( Coffee wity Chat session ) having every alternative  month .\nFee structure and Bus fare is  on higher side and parking space is less on Nidgi schhol.area.",
          "publisher": {
